commit message:
v1.0.1

Add check on first run for su and busybox if not on AOKP

Add simple 1x1 widget

Would like to add at least one more size, and style the 1x1
a bit better, but updating the widget click to open PC works
for now.
Make ADT happy on menu items and seekbars

Large update for v1.0.2

Big nasty reformat of the classes, so hopefully I won't have to
do that again..

Remove VoltageControl if no tables are found.
Theme VoltageControl fragment to match with other fragments.
Add menu button to all fragments for PCSettings which at some point
will have app specific settings.
Add reset and restore options on CPUInfo page.

Need more testing of VoltageControl. One on devices that have
tables at these other locations, two that it consistently works
in testing so far between two devices it does work fine (mV_uV_table)
location.

Fix widget not always updating to right freqs

Widget could not keep up with intents from slider if the user
changed freqs quickly. Update the widget in onPause when we are done
tinkering since we aren't going to see the widget until we leave the
main app anyhow.

Add theme setting to PCSettings

Changes from dark (default) and light themes

Fix a few issues with themes.

Remove alpha from some of the greys. Add images for menu
overflow button. Some other adjustments to prevent
dark text on dark background with the light theme.

Fixup fastcharge detection and usage, add version info to PCSettings
bump version from AOKP version.

for v1.0.3: Refactor/rename - Add simple theming to widget

Widget: Selectable bg color & text color
ColorPicker c/o margaritov
Refactor/rename to brewcrewfoo

Make the widget bg allow user selected colors

Remove widget background images, create a bitmap that can be
colored by the user.
Bump version number before I forget.

Add Android.mk to enable building in the Android source tree.
